---------------------------------------------------------------------
1999 triple CD album from the Indie/Electronic Pop band led by 
singer/songwriter Stephin Merritt. Just as the title promises, 69 Love Songs 
contains just that, most of them sung by Merritt. Guest vocalists include LD 
Beghtol, Glaudio Gonson, Shirley Simms and Dudley Klute.
